snippet: Janelle Monáe held court in her free show of retro-futurist R&B to kick off the 36th Celebrate Brooklyn! series, with an enormous overflow audience.
abstract: Nate Chinen reviews performance by singer Janelle Monae at Prospect Park Bandshell as part of Celebrate Brooklyn! festival.
lead_paragraph: Janelle Monáe held court in her free show of retro-futurist R&B to kick off the 36th Celebrate Brooklyn! series, with an enormous overflow audience.
